#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.lokalize.appdata.xml:8
msgid "Lokalize"
msgstr "Lokalize"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.lokalize.appdata.xml:9
msgid "Computer-aided translation system"
msgstr "Systema de traduction adjutate per le computator"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.lokalize.appdata.xml:11
msgid ""
"Lokalize is the localization tool for KDE software and other free and open "
"source software. It is also a general computer-aided translation system "
"(CAT) with which you can translate OpenDocument files (*.odt). Translate-"
"Toolkit is used internally to extract text for translation from .odt to ."
"xliff files and to merge translation back into .odt file."
msgstr ""
"Lokalize es le instrumento de localisation per le software de KDE e altere "
"software libere e a fonte aperite. Illo anque es un systema de traduction "
"adjutate per le computator (CAT) con le qual tu pote traducer files "
"OpenDocument (*.odt). Translate-Toolkit es usate internemente per extraher "
"texto per traduction ex .odt a .xliff files e fusionar de retorno in file ."
"odt. "

